channel.name: Log 2: Import DB Logs to Excel
channel.description:
It is a simple example of allowing Iguana to serve up data from a SQLite DB to an Excel spreadsheet.
Use it together with "Log 1: Export Logs to DB" which exports the log data used by this channel to SQLite.
http://help.interfaceware.com/v6/excel-import
